&Control
Calculation PAD
Log_file graphite_PAD.log
Console_log true
Output_file graphite_PAD.hdf5
/

&Atomic-wfn
Potential_file /path/to/Atomic_potentials.hdf5
/

&PAD
Input_file graphite.hdf5
E_min -10
E_max 0
E_pixel 0.05
dE 0.1
Initial_state AO
Final_state Calc
Final_state_step 0.01
Polarization Linear
Theta 30
Phi 180
Atomic_orbitals_file /path/to/PAO_and_AO_after_opt.hdf5
/
&Radial-grid 3
0.0025 40
0.005  40
0.01   40000
/
&Phase-shift
Skip_points 10
Calc_points 10
/
